{"tid":1165833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比利時禁止刷首抽，任地獄火紋動物之森手遊下架","createTime":"2019-05-22T05:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T10:41:48.000Z","uid":59328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"764ccf9d6ccb4112bec5c8bbc4d353be2d644b4d","tid":1165833,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=179836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D179836&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=6face704\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=179836</a><br />\n慘啦！比利時毒撚唔可以對著大波5星女角打飛機啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330eb660b42f15b45658519ad017fc367a1647b0","tid":1165833,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"pokemon go果種課金模式值得其他日系手機game學習嗎?"},{"pid":"afb56ae388613e0f0e1ce7e2f3a7ac817cebee1b","tid":1165833,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/23/982d9255cb39a6711f3adf2d5c3zjyf4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F23%2F982d9255cb39a6711f3adf2d5c3zjyf4.JPG&h=da825931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任天堂《聖火降魔錄》及《動物之森》手機遊戲因轉蛋制違反比利時法規 預計 8 月下架<br />\n （巴哈勇者 霹靂卡霹靂拉拉 報導）<br />\n　　任天堂近日宣布，旗下智慧型手機遊戲《聖火降魔錄 英雄雲集》及《動物之森 口袋露營廣場》將在 2019 年 8 月 27 日結束比利時地區的營運。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n　　比利時近來修正相關博奕法令，凡含有轉蛋系統的虛擬遊戲均屬於違法，由於《聖火降魔錄 英雄雲集》及《動物之森 口袋露營廣場》均屬於免費下載遊戲並含有轉蛋機制，因此任天堂決定在今年 8 月 27 日下架上述兩款遊戲。而 8 月結束營運後，玩家將無法於比利時的應用程式商店中下載上述兩款遊戲。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n　　同時比利時任天堂也表示「今後，具有類似營運模式的遊戲也將不會在比利時上市。」而此次消息目前暫不影響其他歐洲國家之遊戲營運。"},{"pid":"cba1e6345bb57db2f2b33d128fddde4a29be1e28","tid":1165833,"uid":64009,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"鬼佬on9<br />\n撚係賭博<br />\n都無得贏錢<br />\n抵佢地無手遊玩要on99玩過氣console"},{"pid":"514d439a6a0a3b955e8f20012c1dd0642a919359","tid":1165833,"uid":105166,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"cba1e6345bb57db2f2b33d128fddde4a29be1e28","tid":1165833,"uid":64009,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"鬼佬on9<br />\n撚係賭博<br />\n都無得贏錢<br />\n抵佢地無手遊玩要on99玩過氣console"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"弱智仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同賭博個原理/心理一樣㗎，人地進步禁咗係好事呀。比啲遊戲商導緊你都唔撚知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec2ab39317883c3ac13eb864c8469fb70fe4a81","tid":1165833,"uid":193421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cba1e6345bb57db2f2b33d128fddde4a29be1e28","tid":1165833,"uid":64009,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"鬼佬on9<br />\n撚係賭博<br />\n都無得贏錢<br />\n抵佢地無手遊玩要on99玩過氣console"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"獎品一定要係錢先叫賭博？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ae397efbbad0325234f5f80a259826ec90112e","tid":1165833,"uid":54557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cba1e6345bb57db2f2b33d128fddde4a29be1e28","tid":1165833,"uid":64009,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"鬼佬on9<br />\n撚係賭博<br />\n都無得贏錢<br />\n抵佢地無手遊玩要on99玩過氣console"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:07:40.000Z","msg":"有抽獎成份嘅都係啦<br />\n如果唔係點解香港抽獎要攞牌"},{"pid":"89dd440f095aa8d8e5295d91fcc666f5b4bcb976","tid":1165833,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"330eb660b42f15b45658519ad017fc367a1647b0","tid":1165833,"uid":66618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"pokemon go果種課金模式值得其他日系手機game學習嗎?"},"citedB